---
// Componente Footer - Pie de página del sitio
---

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="footer-content">
      {/* Columna 1 - Información */}
      <div class="footer-column footer-left">
        <h3 class="footer-title">Exportadora Surberries</h3>
        <p class="footer-text">
          Más que exportar fruta, conectamos origen, calidad y cumplimiento para llevar berries congelados de Chile al mundo.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Columna 2 - Logo Chile (Centro) */}
      <div class="footer-column footer-center">
        <img 
          src="/images/logo-chile-exportador.png" 
          alt="Chile Exportador" 
          class="chile-logo"
        />
      </div>

      {/* Columna 3 - Contacto (Derecha) */}
      <div class="footer-column footer-right">
        <h3 class="footer-title">Contacto</h3>
        <div class="footer-contact">
          <div class="contact-item">📍 Isabel Riquelme #506 - Chillán - Chile</div>
          <div class="contact-item">📧 contacto@exportsurberries.cl</div>
          <a href="https://wa.me/56959008508?text=Hola,%20me%20interesa%20contactar%20a%20Surberries" 
             class="contact-item contact-link" 
             target="_blank" 
             rel="noopener noreferrer">
            📱 +56 9 5900 8508
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Línea divisoria */}
    <div class="footer-divider"></div>

    {/* Copyright */}
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p class="footer-copyright">
        © {new Date().getFullYear()} <a href="https://nxchile.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="nxchile-link">nxChile</a> para Exportadora Surberries. Todos los derechos reservados.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    background-color: #1A1A1A;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    padding: 3rem 0 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .footer-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .footer-column {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-left {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .footer-center {
    text-align: center;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .footer-right {
    text-align: right;
    align-items: flex-end;
  }

  .chile-logo {
    height: 120px;
    width: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .footer-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #FFD700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .footer-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #B0B0B0;
        /* Limitar a 3 líneas */
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 3;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }

  .footer-contact {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-item {
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #B0B0B0;
  }

  .contact-link {
    color: #B0B0B0;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    color: #00A86B;
  }

  .footer-divider {
    border-top: 1px solid #333333;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .footer-copyright {
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #777777;
  }

  .nxchile-link {
    color: #FFD700;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .nxchile-link:hover {
    color: #FFE44D;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .footer-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer-left,
    .footer-center,
    .footer-right {
      text-align: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 2rem 0 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>